REMOTE DOWNLOAD NOT AVAILABLE - please contact data@library.columbia.edu for access. Tibet Provincial Capital Location and Census Data, 2000 is a point theme representing the capital of Tibet province in China in 2000.  Attribute information includes population variables from the China 2000 census. 

This data layer is part of the 2000 Tibet Township Population Census Data with GIS Maps data set produced by the All China Marketing Research Co. and distributed by the University of Michigan, China Data Center.
